{"tid":759080,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚憎搭公共交通工具，車未停定啲人已經起身","createTime":"2018-07-28T09:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T17:36:12.000Z","uid":63113,"like":16,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c103e80ca3a35899c80fd03663cc12380b9027","tid":759080,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:31:46.000Z","msg":"有啲誇張到 到站前一個彎位速度唔慢都起身夠膽玩碰碰車<br />\n<br />\n好多老人家咁做<br />\n<br />\n年中䟿低唔少又懶司機 唔反省下自己急乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfe8c4f634e50d1dab42df56814471ff9f8d971","tid":759080,"uid":52946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:33:46.000Z","msg":"巴士成日係咁 車站仲有幾分鍾班人就狗沖"},{"pid":"fe1620adf2f3e4e2c9898d76c015e6526afb5b61","tid":759080,"uid":149487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:33:52.000Z","msg":"成日都係咁<br />\n我又無跌底"},{"pid":"c837f9b333c1dd618046a3ab6f6621a1aa0ec16a","tid":759080,"uid":82450,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:49:26.000Z","msg":"未開門已經推鳩你<br />\n次次都紮實個馬用背脊頂返佢"},{"pid":"90162bf1e847d782977081158eaa90661ff3e976","tid":759080,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T10:20:35.000Z","msg":"搭車搭船搭飛機都係啦<br />\n車未停定<br />\n船未停定<br />\n飛機未熄安全帶燈<br />\n唔應該離開座位<br />\n任何唔係咁做嘅人我都當佢幼稚園未畢業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0959413272d59b92042dda88cff3b9e987e9a7","tid":759080,"uid":66242,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T10:22:43.000Z","msg":"加多句<br />\n電梯上唔應該行走<br />\n左行右企係上世紀嘅落後做法<br />\n同埋老弱婦孺係唔應該使用電梯"},{"pid":"e3d9caf8d56218008cebf6c171ff1b060ea63769","tid":759080,"uid":196099,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T10:23:10.000Z","msg":"巴士有時都可以體諒嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時轉車站轉車特別係新界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔